    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The CFD model for CPB hemolysis prediction is accepted for the stated COU. Seven factors were assessed and the assessment team is satisfied that the model meets the requirements for a Class II device at MRL 2. Six factors were not assessed in accordance with MRL 2 scoping. The overall evidence base supports the conclusion that the model can reliably identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions within the stated uncertainty bounds.",
